When aggregate demand spikes during a severe heat wave, for instance, the rigid grid struggles.

58:18.020 --> 58:22.860
Frequencies deviate, voltages drop, and the system fails into rolling blackouts.

58:23.120 --> 58:25.560
It is a fragile, linear system.

58:25.780 --> 58:25.980
Right.

