We've all experienced that.

58:27.220 --> 58:33.520
What if we re-architected the entire grid to function as a macroscopic flash reluctance engine?

58:33.520 --> 58:35.280
That is a massive leap.

58:36.020 --> 58:40.440
How would slope-based constraint enforcement actually work on a grid level?

58:40.800 --> 58:44.360
Imagine if entire cities ceased to be passive consumers.

58:45.040 --> 58:54.680
What if millions of smart homes, distributed battery banks, and connected electric vehicles function collectively as the distributed electromagnetic constraint enforcers?

58:54.800 --> 58:56.520
So we are the auto-tune.

58:56.520 --> 58:57.260
Exactly.

