And simultaneously, millions of smart appliances dynamically shed load by skipping a cooling cycle, completely mirroring the conditional injection survival mechanism we talked about.

59:49.660 --> 59:51.440
Skipping a beat so the core can recover.

59:51.440 --> 59:55.520
The grid stops being a dumb pipe pushing electrons.

59:56.080 --> 59:59.720
It becomes a breathing, self-aware, self-healing entity.

